				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Here is another 35min hard ldon parse for you to ponder: 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">
<br />
Magician + pet, me:  195404 
<br />

<br />
Wizard VT + few elementals, emp robe: 202597 
<br />

<br />
Paladin MT + excelent gear, full aa's 172230 (that includes 54k from slay undead) 
<br />
</span>
<br />

<br />
--- 
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">I cannied 62 pets</span>, I was in full burn all the time. Nuke as fast as you can, canni between pulls. Pet uptime was about 98%, so no canning would bring roughly 2% more pet dps.
<br />

<br />
My canni is pretty good, I have 15% mana save from e-sleevs and summoning haste 2 aa + 18% from my e-boots and pet is focused by GODS and after that I switch to e-hands to get SV saving. 
<br />

<br />
Without that canni, you can take half of my nuke damage away, <span style="font-weight: bold">leaving me at 135k damage done including the pet. </span>
<br />

<br />
I'm more than willing to post this parse, showing that I did not slack, this was maximum effiency play. Without canni , I drop down to paladin levels. 
<br />
That is not acceptable for mare few point internal mana regen. We were all in similar gear level and AA level.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">
<br />
How can you say this does not make me a really sad grouping class?</span>
<br />

<br />
Please think what we can bring to a group?
<br />

<br />
Our pets cant offtank 900 hitting mobs.
<br />
Our DS is pretty medicore damage dealing factor against hard ldon mobs.
<br />
Our coth is pretty useless in groups, granted it saves many bad pulls, but the group has to be good to use coth as escape method.
<br />
We can only give 7.2 per tick rods, that have no wears message. People click it at max 3-5 per tick effiency.
<br />

<br />
We have no snare, no root as crowd control.
<br />
We have no evac.
<br />
We can not heal.
<br />
We have no buffs.
<br />
Our summons are useless, usually only one needing dmg bracer is the cleric.
<br />

<br />
And now we are not even good damage. How in the hell are we in balance with other int casters?
<br />

<br />
You know how we nuke, we nuke like druids with SCS3. 
<br />
You know our pet DPS are hugely hit by high AC and high levels of mobs available.
<br />
You well know we have 2 usefull pets out of 4.
<br />
You well know our fire and earth pets are not used at all in groups, later one sometimes while yo-yo root soloign or up front chaining.
<br />

<br />
AND I have to say, you know what damage we do in groups now without canni. 
<br />

<br />
How can you say we are still a good grouping class?
<br />

<br />
We are now pretty sad class indeed. And we solo like shit also.
<br />

<br />
Not to mention, its kinda sad that you include water form 3, that costs us 3 + 6 + 9 to max out to gain 4 per tick.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=338533">Gareon</a> Arch Convoker of Venril Sathir.</span><span class="gensmall"><br /><br />Last edited by gareon on Wed Dec 17, 2003 1:28 pm; edited 7 times in total</span></td>
