				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Rytan,
<br />

<br />
Not to be a nit, but one of you calculations is off for standard mage mana regen (non-pet cani).
<br />

<br />
Trans Rods, cast by self.
<br />
400 mana pre-spec to cast, 360x3 mana returned.
<br />

<br />
Without spec, that's around 4.5 mana/tick.
<br />
With a spec savings of around 25% (est), it's 5.2 mana/tick
<br />

<br />
Claims of Mana regen being 7+ mana/tick with Trans Rods are only possible using someone else to cast it for you, OR using mage elemental pants (circumventing the need to actually have to expend the mana to make one).</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
