Pet-canni sheet
<br />
<a href="http://forum.magecompendium.com/tower/viewtopic.php?t=3882" target="_blank">http://forum.magecompendium.com/tower/viewtopic.php?t=3882</a>
<br />

<br />
I do know I figured a Shaman at about 55FT for canni IV and Q and add in canni V every 3 min and it’s more than that. BUT the shaman needs time to spend his mana also so his effective FT is lower.
<br />

<br />
One other factor. Magicians must stand for part of any fight if they send in pet or there is very good chance they will get siting argo. This is much more true for them than none pet classes. This reduces med rate so please factor this in as well.
<br />

<br />
I do hope this points out some other things that may not have been considered. Also note: IRE could be left alone and give "controlled" pet cani mana regen as it is not afected by pet HP.
<br />

